sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Notebook Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Auth
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet<br/>10250/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant NotebookPod as Jupyter Notebook Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Culling as Culling Controller<br/>Idle Detection
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Kubelet: Flow 1: Notebook Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: User credentials<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>Notebook Created<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: POST StatefulSet<br/>POST Service<br/>POST VirtualService (if Istio)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>Kubelet: Create Pod<br/>HTTPS/10250 mTLS
        Kubelet-->>K8sAPI: Pod Running
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>StatefulSet Ready
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH Notebook Status<br/>Ready Replicas Update
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Culling,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Notebook Culling (Idle Detection)
        loop Every IDLENESS_CHECK_PERIOD (default: 1 min)
            Culling->>NotebookPod: GET /api/kernels<br/>HTTP/8888 No Auth
            NotebookPod-->>Culling: JSON: [{last_activity: timestamp}]
            alt Idle > CULL_IDLE_TIME (default: 1440 min)
                Culling->>K8sAPI: PATCH Notebook CR<br/>Add: kubeflow-resource-stopped annotation<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
                K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>Notebook Annotated
                Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH StatefulSet<br/>Set replicas: 0<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
            end
        end
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        loop Every scrape_interval
            Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 No Auth
            Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics<br/>notebook_created_total<br/>notebook_failed_total<br/>notebook_culled_total
        end
    end
